message.body: There's even more potatoes left today than yesterday. Guessing you're all set, but should I take some home for you?

I'm not sick of them but won't be over that way until at least wends to pick them up. Kinda busy beginning of the week. If D's around u could drop some off but it might not be necessary because I probably can't get them for awhile.
Thanks for continuing to look out for me :)
I wound up taking them just in case. Will see if my friend Michelle wants em. Working again Wed night. When y'all heading to NY?
I don't know yet if we are for sure.
Ok, well maybe we can grab a beer or something over the week. Might go record shopping with D on Friday. It's my birthday & figured I'd treat myself!
Nice, happy bday! We will have to meet up for a beer for sure
Great! Enjoy your night and see you over the next days:-)
